# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# 请勿在仓库根目录执行 npm；若误生成请勿提交
/node_modules/
/.next/

# frontend — 详见 frontend/.gitignore（node_modules、.next 等仅在 frontend/）

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript（根目录若产生）
*.tsbuildinfo

# backend — Python
backend/.venv/
backend/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
